[I] Jakarta Commons Logging

[T] The Logging package is an ultra-thin bridge between different
[T] logging libraries. Commons components may use the Logging API
[T] to remove compile-time and run-time dependencies on any particular
[T] logging package, and contributors may write Log implementations
[T] for the library of their choice.

[U] https://jakarta.apache.org/commons/logging/

[A] Apache Jakarta Commons team
[M] Minto van der Sluis <minto@multimach.com>

[C] extra/development

[L] OpenSource
[V] 1.3.6

[D] 0281a3fefe935f3ae7ed2533256a39147901a1de53876a0d37db1462 commons-logging-1.3.6-src.tar.gz https://dlcdn.apache.org//commons/logging/source/

. $base/package/*/*/java-conf.in BUILD_TYPE=ANT
buildtarget="compile javadoc"
buildjardir=target
builddocdir=dist/docs
